data.description: Fantastic Palm Beach Gardens Location!!. Concrete DiVosta Garden Lakes Townhouse w/Extra Den or possible 3rd Br (with adding closet and door) downstairs. Nicely maintained and clean, all set to make it your own. Very rare GAS Stove!!!  2018 Kitchen, appliances, AC & Floor. 2022 Master Bathroom & Hot Water Heater, new Washer & Dryer. Storm Accordion Shutters, Low HOA Fees of just $200/mo, 2 assigned parking spaces, pet friendly - 2 dogs or 2 cats per unit. Community is tucked away but next to Publix, Shopping, Restaurants, PGA Blvd, Gardens Mall, Beaches. Centrally located. Ready to go! Call Today.
